Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
45 Ainslie Avenue, Braddon is located in the exciting new inner-city precinct of Founders Lane on the door stop of the CBD. This perfectly desired location is a stone's throw away from the Canberra Centre and the heart of the CBD.

Available for lease is 109sqm* of ground floor retail space with great street frontage onto Cooyong St.
The property boasts a wide permitted use making it suitable for a broad range of operators including but not limited to:

- Retailers
- Service providers
- Food operators

Surrounded by residential developments, now is the time to establish your business in this offering in a thriving location.

For more information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE Canberra.

Approx*â€ƒ

24-26 Mort Street is located within one of Canberra's most popular and vibrant precincts. The property is situated in a fantastic location surrounded by various commercial offices, some of Canberra's best retailers, restaurants, cafes, residential apartments and Hotels. The Canberra Center is a short walk away as well as the City Bus Interchange.  The property boasts a wide permitted use making it suitable for a broad range of operators including but not limited to:

- Retailers
- Service providers
- Food operators
- Health practitioners/Medical operators

The building has undergone extensive works and will shortly commence internal upgrades. A new lift will be installed to service the first floor tenancies and plans are underway to activate the lane way between the two buildings.

Strong public transport links are available with a bus stop situated directly in front of the building as well as public visitor car parking. The future light rail stops are a short walk away. Ample onsite reserved parking is available.

Available for Lease:

102sqm*- Frontage onto Mort Street 

The flexible floor plate allows the space to be altered to meet various businesses requirements.  Each unit has provision for grease trap, sewer and plumbing.

For further information on this exciting opportunity please contact CBRE.

*Approx.

32 Mort Street is situated in the new Yamoroshi mixed use Development which makes a statement on Mort Street.  Braddon has seen constant development creating a demand for additional amenity to support the increasing population in the area.  The area already offers restaurants, entertainment, health and wellbeing services and retail.  

The Yamoroshi Development offers a mix of retail & commercial space.  Unit 7 is located in the development through an internal laneway which offers boutique suites and ability for outdoor seating.

Highlight features include;
- Ground floor alleyway unit
- 92sqm* with 3sqm* tiled space directly out front
- Glass Shopfront
- Dedicated parking on site
- 3 Underground car parks
- suitable for a range of users including restaurant, bar, shop, professional office

Surrounded by offices, residential units and hotels, now is the time to establish your business in this boutique offering in a thriving location.

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE.

*Approx.

35 Lonsdale Street  is a brand new mixed-use development prominently located on the corner of Lonsdale and Girrahween Street. 

This prominent location, directly across from Haig Park offers boutique ground floor units suitable to retail, cafe, restaurant, or personal services. Spaces are cold shell and ready for fitout.

Available for lease:

Unit 1: 85sqm* 
Unit 2: 154sqm* 
Unit 3: 82sqm*

Units 2 & 3 can be combined to create 238sqm*


For more information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE Canberra.
